      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic and reliable ride! It's in great shape and has been well-maintained, offering a smooth driving experience and a clean interior that\u2019s ready for its next owner. While it shows some light, honest wear from careful use, it remains a solid and dependable vehicle that you can count on for years to come.",
