    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though a discerning eye might find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper\u2014purely cosmetic and consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery remains plush and free of tears, with only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster. All power features, from the panoramic sunroof to the dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers consistent power, backed by a comprehensive service history. We recently fitted a new set of all-season tires and performed a full fluid flush. This car isn't just a mode of transport; it's a testament to responsible ownership. Ready for its next chapter with a buyer who appreciates quality without the showroom price tag.",
